definition: many/much/often/a lot of/numerous/more/in excess/how (to what extent)/multi-/Taiwan pr. [duo2] when it means "how"

sentences.english: Few foods can hold a candle to this leafy green.

sentences.english: A dose calculation algorithm for MLC based conformal radiotherapy is described in this paper.

sentences.english: Leaves are small, felty, gray-green and many-lobed.

sentences.english: How much are the leafy vegetables?
